  <span id="freeText14585075401499243474" style="display:none">IN AN ALTERNATE UNIVERSE<br /><br /><br />Marcel eats the madeleine. <br /><br />Marcel : Oh, that really reminds me of something...<br /><br />Marcel's friend : Oh yes? What?<br /><br />Marcel : ….. I can't quite put my finger on it....er….hmmm. No, it's gone.<br /><br />Marcel's friend: Oh well. It probably wasn't that important.</span>
