<div id="review_680367941" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680367941" />
    <a title="Sunny" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8549273-sunny"><img alt="Sunny" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1407851057p2/8549273.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/680367941?book_show_action=true">Jul 29, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Sunny" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Sunny" href="/user/show/8549273-sunny">Sunny</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9781300969518" href="/book/show/18268658-in-search-of-lost-time">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8549273-sunny?shelf=1315-read">1315-read</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8549273-sunny?shelf=nook">nook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/8549273-sunny?shelf=all-boxall">all-boxall</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer680367941" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9345488648045430697">In another LIST book (<a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/447043594' rel='nofollow noopener'>1Q84</a>) it was said that unless you have the opportunity to be in jail or have to hide out for a long time, you can&apos;t read the whole of <i>In Search of Lost Time</i>.<br/><br/><a href='http://s1257.photobucket.com/user/TravellingSunny/media/GoodReads%20Pics/challengeaccepted_zps78343d71.png.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
