</a><br/><br/>Volume 1. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680369621' rel='nofollow noopener'>Swann’s Way</a> (★★★★☆)<br/>Volume 2. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680369899' rel='nofollow noopener'>Within a Budding Grove</a> (★★★☆☆)<br/>Volume 3. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680370025' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Guermantes Way</a> (★★☆☆☆)<br/>Volume 4. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680370135' rel='nofollow noopener'>Cities of the Plain</a> (★★★★★)<br/>Volume 5. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680370458' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Captive</a> (★★★★★)<br/>Volume 6. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680370690' rel='nofollow noopener'>The Fugitive</a> (★★★★☆)<br/>Volume 7. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/680370879' rel='nofollow noopener'>Time Regained</a> (★★★★★)<br/><br/><a href='http://s1257.photobucket.com/user/TravellingSunny/media/GoodReads%20Pics/Challengecompleted_zps913edfb4.png.html' target='_blank' rel='nofollow noopener'>
