  <span id="freeText9345488648045430697" style="display:none">In another LIST book (<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/447043594" rel="nofollow noopener">1Q84</a>) it was said that unless you have the opportunity to be in jail or have to hide out for a long time, you can't read the whole of <i>In Search of Lost Time</i>.<br><br><a href="http://s1257.photobucket.com/user/TravellingSunny/media/GoodReads%20Pics/challengeaccepted_zps78343d71.png.html" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">
