<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/40378238-lost-time"><img alt="Lost Time: Lectures on Proust in a Soviet Prison Camp" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1551194775l/40378238._SX98_.jpg" />
